casebody.data:
Robert H. AJAMIAN, petitioner,
v.
Edward DOMINGUEZ, et al. No. 16-8333. Supreme Court of the United States April 24, 2017.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Justice GORSUCH took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
